    	<description>ClicAndTag, Cloud and Mobile Platform for Business Management

A complete Platform
•	Mange all your business in one place
	-	Accounting
	-	Quotation and Invoices
	-	Collaborative agenda
	-	Time Management
	-	Digital safe
	-	Expenses
•	And for any support!
	-	Computer, tablet, smartphone...
	-	Free dedicated apps available for smartphones 

A clever Platform
•	Synthetic dashboards: access to relevant statistics and quickly visualize the health of your business
•	Mobility: additional applications for your smartphone
•	Work in a collaborative way with your employees, partners and accountant
•	Alerts and regulatory schedules 

A unique platform to improve your business reactivity and productivity!
</description>
